        // ---- "Check current value first" - single-tracking style ----
        // Mirrors UCDR's own flow exactly: the target field's wrapper stays
        // HIDDEN (not just disabled) until Check succeeds, a separate
        // uneditable "Current Value" box shows what's on file today, and only
        // then does the (existing, unmodified) target field appear.
        // editable: true  -> target input is pre-filled with the current
        //                    value and stays editable (like UCDR's own
        //                    "Updated Customer/Instructions Remark" field).
        // editable: false -> target input is a dropdown; it's left blank so
        //                    the user picks a fresh new value (Job Method,
